title: Quake Mission Pack 2: Dissolution of Eternity
description:
Registered version of Mission Pack 2: Dissolution of Eternity for ID Software&#039;s Quake.

This was torrented from somewhere else; however, I couldn&#039;t find the respective torrent, so there you go :^) Full credit to the original uploader, whoever that may be.

quake-doe/ -- base directory
quake-doe/Quake Mission Pack 2: Dissolution of Eternity.bin -- sector dump of the Mission Pack 2 CD
quake-doe/Quake Mission Pack 2: Dissolution of Eternity.ccd -- [don&#039;t even know where ccd stands for in this context] for the sector dump
quake-doe/Quake Mission Pack 2: Dissolution of Eternity.cue -- cuefile for the sector dump
quake-doe/Quake Mission Pack 2: Dissolution of Eternity.sub -- subchannel data for the sector dump

Enjoy :^)
